  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Best roguelike of all time' according to my neighbor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pennylooter's got all this cool stuff check it out:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOSS FIGHTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/bdd4e4a2f9b9be70e29759ede8ddb1ff.poster.avif?t=1757363907\" width=1170 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/bdd4e4a2f9b9be70e29759ede8ddb1ff.webm?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/bdd4e4a2f9b9be70e29759ede8ddb1ff.mp4?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work your way through all 12 bosses, with two difficulty modes just in case you feel like they're going easy on you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REGULAR FIGHTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/20fcbf35740d629923a17438b0c4cb59.poster.avif?t=1757363907\" width=1170 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/20fcbf35740d629923a17438b0c4cb59.webm?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/20fcbf35740d629923a17438b0c4cb59.mp4?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between the boss fights, you'll have to contend with multiple waves of enemies. As you progress, you'll find yourself confronted by more of these ugly creatures, but do not strife! Collect the pennies they drop and you can use them to buy guns, food, and items that give you special abilities. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/49591f87bac872fe4e5fc13dc497a0a4.poster.avif?t=1757363907\" width=1170 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/49591f87bac872fe4e5fc13dc497a0a4.webm?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/49591f87bac872fe4e5fc13dc497a0a4.mp4?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seven different biomes, each with their own unique enemies and surprises. Watch out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/12c13fdda2c161fa4b70566dc2bf042e.webp?t=1757363907\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/12c13fdda2c161fa4b70566dc2bf042e.poster.avif?t=1757363907\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=251 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's frogs.</p>",
