ems that give you special abilities. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/49591f87bac872fe4e5fc13dc497a0a4.poster.avif?t=1757363907\" width=1170 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/49591f87bac872fe4e5fc13dc497a0a4.webm?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/49591f87bac872fe4e5fc13dc497a0a4.mp4?t=1757363907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seven different biomes, each with their own unique enemies and surprises. Watch out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/12c13fdda2c161fa4b70566dc2bf042e.webp?t=1757363907\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057250/extras/12c13fdda2c161fa4b70566dc2bf042e.poster.avif?t=1757363907\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=251 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's frogs.</p>",
